 Was Responding to a Trump Tweet from January. *(03:14:00)** RT @michelledeidre: Useful #Paris #sIrish Embassy +33144176700British Embassy +33144513100US Embassy +33143122222Canadian Embassy +33144432900 #ParisAttacks *(00:38:00)** RT @monteiro: GO FUCK YOURSELF, FUCKING ASSHOLE. https://t.co/OjSL6whazH *(00:40:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Twitter Mentions* RT @doghousemike: @amandapalmer Apparently #porteouvertereIs the Thing to Use for Hooking up Places to stay/friends/etcPass it On!. *(Mentioned by DyanaValentine)* *(01:00:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer It's #porteouverte to Find a place to Sleep in Paris, with a Map https://t.co/HOirDSQym9. *(Mentioned by maguelonne*)_ *(00:50:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer It's Porteouverte ;). *(Mentioned by BillyDesEnfers)* *(00:54:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer Pass it without Using the # or You'll Overload It. *(Mentioned by aries13474)* *(00:57:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer only if You Live in Paris.. *(Mentioned by lookylu)* *(00:58:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>","lines":[13,14],"size":3126,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
